Information
------------------------------

The Coolest Places on Earth 
The Coolest Places on Earth takes viewers on a journey of discovery to the most astonishing places on the planet - cities, festivals, landmarks and jaw-dropping works of nature - exploring each location's history and culture, to discover why it deserves to be called one of the coolest places on earth!





3)  Chile 
Today on The Coolest Places on Earth we're taking a trip to the long country, Chile, the South American nation of extreme contrasts, like bone-dry deserts and luscious waterfalls, snowy mountains and simmering volcanoes, where modern life and ancient history blend and big cities are just minutes away from exotic warm islands and frosty getaways. Que Rico! Here we come!
